A U.S. district judge agreed to take
a $94 million lawsuit against  Barclays Plc (BARC)  out of bankruptcy
court, according to a court filing. Bankrupt  Thornburg Mortgage
Inc. (THMRQ) , now called TMST Inc., accused the U.K. bank of breaching
repurchase agreements.  To contact the reporter on this story:
